Package org.universAAL.middleware.service.owls.process

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Conversion
    A universAAL-specific value function for binding output parameters stating that the given output parameter represents a converted representation of a reachable property.
    OutputBinding
    Support for constructing an OWL-S http://www.daml.org/services/owl-s/1.1/Process.owl#OutputBinding that can be used in the definition of process results according to the universAAL model.
    ProcessEffect
    Support for the universAAL model of process effects.
    ProcessInput
    This class represents the OWL-S process input parameter
    ProcessLocal
    This class represents the OWL-S process local parameter
    ProcessOutput  
    ProcessParameter
    Implementation of process:Parameter (xmlns:process="http://www.daml.org/services/owl-s/1.1/Process.owl#").
    ProcessResult
    This class represents ProcessResult of OWL-S - http://www.daml.org/services/owl-s/1.1/Process.owl#Result
